{"word":"πρόχνῠ","slug":"πρόχνῠ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n90767\" key=\"pro/xnŭ\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πρόχνῠ</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <sense id=\"n90767.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">utterly</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὥς κε . . ἀπόλωνται π. κακῶς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:460\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.460</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; so <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀλέσθαι π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:69\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.69</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n90767.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with the knees forward</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. καθεζομένη</foreign>, i.e. kneeling or crouching, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:570\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.570</biblScope> </bibl> (where <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Πρόγνυ</foreign> shd. perh. be restd., cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γνύπετος</foreign>, Skt. <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">prajñú-</tr_> (dub. sens.)). </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n90767.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> dub. sens. in Antim.Col.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2P\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2P.</biblScope> </bibl>: later, simply <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">πάνυ</ref></xr>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:1118\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.1118</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:249\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.249</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}